headline.print_headline: Goldman Fund Sells Stake in Port Operator SSA Marine
headline.main: Goldman Fund Sells Stake in Port Operator SSA Marine

lead_paragraph: An infrastructure fund run by Goldman Sachs has sold its 49 percent stake in the holding company of SSA Marine, one of the world's largest privately held port operators, SSA said on Tuesday.
